cashstrapped cuba signed a new economic aid 
pact with the soviet union on saturday cubas official news agency 
said soviet exports would be adjusted but it gave no figures 
soviet officials have warned that the crisis in their own 
country would mean significant cuts in aid to cuba whose hardline 
